Today is a bit of a catch up episode to show you the various farms I've been building, projects in the works, and just a bunch of random stuff. We also get to take our first look into VintageBeef's Trading Card Game.

Back from Dentist: No root canals needed! Yay! Just 2 fillings and I am good.
